docs.text: emiweb 🔗 emission web ui 🎤 emiweb is a web UI that you can use to transmit your voice over WebRTC. To start the server make sure you have npm and next.js installed, then run: npm run start Then you can visit http://localhost:13000 by default in your browser and start streaming.

docs.text: Output 🔗 emiweb sends the output using WebRTC to the listener. You need to provide some info about it using environmental variables: EMIWEB_EMIGATE_URL - URL of the target server
